<template>
    <headMenu :menu="menu"/>
</template>

<script scoped>
import headMenu from './headMenu.vue'
import { mapGetters } from 'vuex';
export default {
    mounted() {
        this.menu = this.$store.state.menu;
    },
    components: {
        headMenu,
    },
    computed: {
        ...mapGetters(['menu']),
    },
    data() {
        return {
            menu: '',
            
        };
    }
}
</script>
